    <string name="calibration_section">赤道仪校准</string>
    <string name="calibration_intro">校准分为两种：快速同步适合不想调极轴、只修正当前区域指向；一星/两星/三星校准会让 OnStep 建立指向模型，三星后可继续精调极轴。</string>
    <string name="calibration_target_label">校准星或坐标</string>
    <string name="calibration_target_hint">Vega / M31 / 05:35 -05:23</string>
